Unify, Find, and Manage Your Analytics

Your analytics are now together in an intuitive and personalized home page that you can experience in Analytics Studio and the Analytics Tab. On this centralized home page, you can see the latest changes for your CRM Analytics assets, and dashboards and reports.

To access Analytics home: Legacy Folder Sharing, Run Reports AND Manage Dashboards, Enhanced Folder Sharing, Run Reports AND Create and Customize Dashboards.

Use search and browse to locate your items through keyword search and filters. For You organizes analytics to help you find what youâ€™re looking for quickly.

With CRM Analytics, you can take either a business user path or a builder path, depending on what you want to do, and you can switch paths at any time.

Find Analytics and Insights
Run a CRM Analytics App to View Dashboards and Lenses
Favorite Your Analytics
Set and Send Smart Notifications
Get Scheduled Updates with Email Subscriptions
Monitor Important Metrics with the CRM Analytics Watchlist

You can build dashboards, embed and customize CRM Analytics, create and share CRM Analytics Apps, deploy CRM Analytics Industry Apps and Prebuilt Apps.

Develop with CRM Analytics: Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.
title: Unifying CRM Analytics
